    "summary": "This BMS map defines the screen layout for displaying pending authorization details in the CardDemo application. It includes fields for card number, authorization date/time, response, amount, merchant details, and other relevant information. The screen also provides options to navigate back, mark/remove fraud, and view the next authorization.",
